sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as ClientApp
    participant KC as Keycloak
    participant Kong as KongGateway
    participant API as FastAPIBackend

    Client->>KC: OAuth2 PKCE login
    KC-->>Client: authorization code
    Client->>KC: token exchange (code_verifier)
    KC-->>Client: JWT (RS256)

    Client->>Kong: POST /api/ai/request + Bearer JWT
    Kong->>Kong: JWT plugin verify via JWKS
    alt invalid or expired
        Kong-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    else valid
        Kong->>Kong: inject tenant_id + roles headers
        Kong->>API: forward authorized request
        API-->>Client: response
    end
